<h1><img src="images/ChildWorld" alt="">Advanced Lycos searches</h1><br>
<img src="/images/bgline" alt="--------------------------------">
<p>
We are pleased to announce that we are now able to provide Lycos searches
directly from our own Web server. Results from Lycos searches will now
include a button that takes you straight back to the Acorn web server, thus
easing the navigation of the Web.
<p>
We can also offer <a href="lycossimple">simple</a> searches.
<p>

